content:
Those shellfish tongs you're holding,
are they just for collecting shellfish?{短暂停}
I sometimes use them to grab gems...

Many tools are made from gemstones,
because gemstones themselves are very durable.{短暂停}
No, not the one you're holding.

I'm not really into fish or seafood,
nothing beats a nice bowl of meat stew.{短暂停}
Seeing you with those shellfish tongs just made me think of that.
